N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5001.29 - Penalty on delinquent accounts

State Regulations

The commission may impose a penalty of 1 1/2 percent
monthly (18 percent per annum) on any monies due to the commission from sales
agents whose accounts are delinquent over 30 days. Notes
